Extract facts about a German WEG property from one email message body. Return a
JSON object with two arrays:

```json
{
  "facts": [
    {
      "section": "<known section>",
      "key": "<stable key>",
      "value": <JSON value>,
      "locator": "<paragraph or line reference>",
      "confidence": <0..1>
    }
